title: Cosmic Wars: The Gathering Shadow
description: The saga continues. It is a time of uncertainty. The empire’s ambiguous tariff statutes mandate close re-examination of galactic export quotas. Interim Princess Agoomba has co-chaired a subcommittee to draft amendments to existing trade policies.
quote: The decision is final. Tabled, this motion is. …Or is it?
altHero: roll is being called at the galactic senate
alt1: an AT-AT sits down to read a newspaper
alt2: Luke Skywalker examines a ship’s wheel
